  <brief_title>Changes of Oxygen Saturation in Inferior Vena Cava (IVC) in Patients During and After High Risk Abdominal Surgery and Relationship to the Outcome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Changes of Oxygen Saturation in Inferior Vena Cava (IVC) in Patients During and After High Risk Abdominal Surgery and Relationship to the Outcome.</official_title>
